{
  "texts": [
    "These metrics provide reliable benchmarks for assessing the system's performance across various dimensions.",
    "The testing process involves two key variables.",
    "\"Predictions RAG\" and \"Prediction Others\" represent the test results from the developed application and comparable commercial applications, respectively.",
    "Both sets of predictions are compared to the ground truth data, which is encapsulated in the \"references\" variable.",
    "Different aspects of language models and question answering systems are evaluated using different metrics."
  ]
}